[[include :scp-wiki-cn:theme:basalt darkmode=a]]

[[module CSS]]
:root {
  --header-title: "𝕐 AI";
  --header-subtitle: "托布兰企业有限公司所属";
  --main-content-width: 100vw;
  --main-content-side-margin: 0;
  --main-content-top-margin: 0;
  --really-ease-out: 0, 0.99, 0, 1;
  --kinda-ease-out: 0.32, 0.83, 0.31, 0.82;
  --basalt-background-color: 0, 0, 0;
  --logo: url(https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/fragment%3Ay-ai-1/y-ai-1.png);
}

body {
  background-color: linear-gradient(to bottom, #fff4e2 49%, black 51%);
  color: #750001;
}

#header {
  position: fixed;
}

#page-title {
  display: none !important;
}

.screen-sized-panel {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100vh;
}

.hero {
  position: relative;
}

.hero-flex {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  position: absolute;
  width: 100vw;
  height: 100vh;
}

.hero h1 {
  font-size: 25vw;
  line-height: 1;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
}


.hero h2 {
  font-size: 3vw;
  max-width: 80%;
}

.screen-sized-panel {
  font-size: 200%;
}

.main-text {
  font-size: 2.75rem;
  padding: 40px;
}

.make-font-smaller {
  font-size: 2rem;
}

.side-by-side {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-evenly;
  align-items: center;
  height: 100%;
}

.force-center {
  justify-content: center;
  height: 100vh;
}

.side-by-side img {
  max-height: 100vh;
  max-width: 50%;
}

.shrink-img {
  max-width: 50%;
}

.dark-panel {
  color: #ffceb1;
}

.one-character {
  font-size: 30vw;
  line-height: 1;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .side-by-side {
     flex-direction: column;
     justify-content: center;
  }

  .main-text {
    font-size: 2rem;
  }

  .make-font-smaller {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .side-by-side img {
    max-width: 75%;
    margin: -10%;
  }

  .hero h2 {
     font-size: 9vw;
  }

  .one-character {
    font-size: 30vh;
  }
}
[[/module]]




[[div_ class="screen-sized-panel hero" style="background-color: #fff4e2"]]

[[div style="font-size: 50%; float: right;"]]
[[module Rate]]
[[/div]]

[[div_ class="hero-flex"]]
+ 𝕐 AI
++ 心胜于物，机胜于人。
[[/div]]
[[/div]]
[[div_ class="screen-sized-panel" style="background-color: #ffe2b3"]]
[[div class="side-by-side"]]
[[div class="main-text"]]
人类是**复杂的**。
[[/div]]
[[image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/fragment%3Ay-ai-1/people-are-confusing.svg]]
[[/div]]
[[/div]]
[[div_ class="screen-sized-panel" style="background-color: #f9c48c"]]
[[div class="side-by-side"]]
[[image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/fragment%3Ay-ai-1/scary-earth.svg class="shrink-img"]]
[[div class="main-text make-font-smaller"]]
在这我们愈发全球化的世界中，我们已度过了大半个21世纪，诸如恐怖组织“乱穿马路者”等团体可能利用这种复杂性来威胁您、您的财产和您的家庭。
[[/div]]
[[/div]]
[[/div]]
[[div_ class="screen-sized-panel" style="background-color: #cf9355"]]
[[div class="side-by-side"]]
[[div class="main-text"]]
为消除此等复杂性，我们创立了颅骨优选评分。
[[/div]]

[[image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/fragment%3Ay-ai-1/skull-select-score.svg]]
[[/div]]
[[/div]]
[[div_ class="screen-sized-panel dark-panel" style="background-color: #8f5f2e;"]]
[[div class="side-by-side"]]
[[image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/fragment%3Ay-ai-1/trust.svg class="shrink-img"]]
[[div class="main-text"]]

颅骨优选评分是对一个人类可信度的数字化标志。
[[/div]]
[[/div]]
[[/div]]
[[div_ class="screen-sized-panel dark-panel" style="background-color: #432e19;"]]
[[div class="side-by-side force-center"]]
[[div class="main-text"]]
让您用快捷又方便的办法看清谁该信。
[[/div]]
[[div_ class="one-character"]]
✔
[[/div]]
[[/div]]
[[/div]]
[[div_ class="screen-sized-panel dark-panel" style="background-color: #221b15;"]]
[[div class="side-by-side force-center"]]
[[div_ class="one-character"]]
✘
[[/div]]
[[div class="main-text"]]
而谁又不该信。
[[/div]]
[[/div]]
[[/div]]
[[div_ class="screen-sized-panel dark-panel" style="background-color: #000000;"]]
[[div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; height: 100%; text-align: center;"]]
[[div class="main-text"]]
今天就注册颅骨优选评分。
[[/div]]
[[div class="main-text"]]
由GREP出品。
[[/div]]
[[/div]]


[[/div]]


